Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,December 16th, X784. Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The boat is almost ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but, um... What about Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothin' to say to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got balls, setting foot \Non the guild's sacred ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,without permission and while in exile...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I heard about his battle with Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he saved your lives by shielding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must acknowledge his efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, they were the actions of a \Nperson who's unaffiliated with the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a harsh judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he's protected \Nthe guild all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just lent a hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got no other purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:04.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was traveling in the area and \Nonly dropped by on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never intended to stay long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Old Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is. That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I had to see that \Ndisapproving look one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a weird wind. And it reeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Got just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here Lucy, you can eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What'd you pull that out for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold Hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably just Lucy's stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! This world's Lucy's stomach \Nmakes that kind of noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gajeel! Try to speak \Nwith a little more delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in that case, I'd better prepare \Na heaping helping for her meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I was just kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, it was \Na strange rumbling sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? Now I can hear heavy breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, what are you sitting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I... A chair, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When'd you get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia let Zeref get away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's fitting she that become \Na chair for Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm not into that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Wendy. Thanks for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-san, you're hurt, too. \NYou shouldn't be serving...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's okay. I enjoy doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my big sister! What a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for, wench?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Man! Man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at you makes my blood boil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... After you got all weepy \Nwhen we were trapped by that tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more word and I'm turning you to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two really get along...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's roar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not thunder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some loud roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An old wound's acting up on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt. {\i1}It's{\i0} coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Heads up, everyone! Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what's wrong... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A real dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still dragons alive after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Dragon of the Apocalypse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the one called Acnologia...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Real dragons still exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:17.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Do you know where Igneel is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Grandine and Metalicana, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:27.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke it! I know I told \Nyou how I got this arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, how my whole body got like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It basically all happened in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:44.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My left arm and leg, and \Nmy internal organs, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of \Nguy this Igneel fellow is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the black one is an enemy of \Nhumanity. Of that, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:58.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus... A human can't beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of dragon \NNatsu and the others love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an evil one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard is humanity's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are we gonna fight it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You're lookin' at this \Nthe wrong way, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about winning \Nor losing with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, how are we gonna escape from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:36.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more like, which of \Nus are gonna survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sayin' this thing \Nis gonna kill some of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...? The whole \Nforest is just... gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How powerful is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:45.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It did this \Nwith its roar alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! What, is it admiring its work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:58.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was its way of \Nintroducing itself, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all still alive, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get off this island right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Get your asses to the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! We're all going home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! I thought you could talk to dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that only I can talk to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All dragons have a high \Nlevel of intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bickslow! Fried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It cut us off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not using words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...because it thinks of humans \Nas nothing more than insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:17.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would speak to vermin. \NIt's the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And no one would bother using their \Nfull strength against vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things in this world \Nyou just can't fight against.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humankind is going to learn that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva?! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like another long \Njourney is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This age is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! There's no way he'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened to \Nyou, the guild would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the circumstances, we should also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare make light of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna ignore your master's \Norders even to the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the enemy, I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus! What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears are hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sad because someone's gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has sadness ever killed a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The answers are deep in \Neach of your hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My proud little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're not gettin' past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause my brats are behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time... I \Nacted like a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?! You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was against it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do you think the people \Nin your guild would run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:00.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving a senile old fool behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morons! All the power you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody who says "I don't have any \Nmore than this", I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine your puny Fairy Tail \Npowers with my lightning attack
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and let's knock this bastard for a loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel! Blumenblatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Freeze Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Nebula!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid Script Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a long time since the \NRaijinshuu fought together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really let 'im have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned monster! You took everything \Nwe got and you're still grinnin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, last chance to take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, that asshole! I'm gonna \Nbeat the crap outta him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, later...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not using the power that \Nit did when it fought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just playing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ascended again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It's as healthy as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we gave it all we had...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we had the power of \Nthree dragon slayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with concentrating the entire \Nguild's power together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some help Dragon Slayer Magic is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it intend to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll just go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it means to \Nwipe out the whole island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it gonna end for all of us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who can use defensive \Nmagic, go full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to draw runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of other kinds of defensive \Nmagic you can do with letter based magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Focus all your magic \Npower on the Fried and Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hold hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let it end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I refuse to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, join your power together as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show this creature \Nthe bond of our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Let's all go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, huh, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,December 16th, X784. Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:49.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia annihilated the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Acnologia disappeared once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A search was conducted in the surrounding \Nsea for the following six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but no survivors were to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, seven years passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. I remember we were \Nattacked by the black dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then we all got surrounded by \Nthis glowing light, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think maybe we all died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Fairy Tail could \Nbe killed off so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Fairy Tail, X791
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just track \Neveryone down and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right. Let's all \Ngo home together, to the guild.
